    <item>
      <title>Ric 21</title>
      <link>https://ric-unknownartist.projektemacher.org/tags/ric-21/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ric-unknownartist.projektemacher.org/tags/ric-21/</guid>
      <description>The motif of this print is the Kaiser Wilhelm Memorial Church . It&amp;rsquo;s the only currently known work of Ric showing Berlin.&#xA;Reconstructed from Google Maps the view is from Tauentzienstraße.</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ric 27</title>
      <link>https://ric-unknownartist.projektemacher.org/tags/ric-27/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ric-unknownartist.projektemacher.org/tags/ric-27/</guid>
      <description>The motif of this print is certainly the Le Moulin de la Galette (Moulin du Radet) in Paris.&#xA;More on windmills in Montmartre:&#xA;Windmills of Montmatre Lost Windmills of Paris </description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ric 29</title>
