      <guid>https://ric-unknownartist.projektemacher.org/tags/ric-29/</guid>
      <description>The motif of this print is the Pont des Arts in Paris. The bridge was painted / drawn by various artists. Partly also from the perspective shown here.&#xA;A similar perspective on Google Maps .</description>
